3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes joint design of power allocation and beamformers to optimize energy-efficiency subject to user quality-of-service constraints, which is a problem in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the use of beamforming to improve the quality of wireless communication, which is relevant to multimedia applications.
